description: Global X ETF Series II - Global X S&P Crude Oil Futures Enhanced ER ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Mirae Asset Global Investments (Hong Kong) Limited. It invests in the commodity market. The fund uses derivatives such as future contracts to invest in WTI crude oil. It seeks to replicate the performance of the S&P GSCI Crude Oil Enhanced Index Excess Return, by investing in commodity as per the weighting in the index. Global X ETF Series II - Global X S&P Crude Oil Futures Enhanced ER ETF was formed on June 10, 2016 and is domiciled in Hong Kong.
name: Global X S&P Crude Oil Futures Enhanced ER ETF (HKD)
